1
00:00:05,704 --> 00:00:08,400
<i>Press down hard on the gas</i>

2
00:00:08,474 --> 00:00:12,342
<i>That's right, there's no compromise</i>

3
00:00:12,411 --> 00:00:16,404
<i>We'll slip through the night</i>

4
00:00:16,749 --> 00:00:19,240
<i>At the final moment push hard</i>

5
00:00:19,318 --> 00:00:23,379
<i>That's right, all the way to zero,</i>

6
00:00:23,455 --> 00:00:27,414
<i>Until we wipe away the days</i>

7
00:00:28,894 --> 00:00:33,627
<i>Gently open your heart</i>

8
00:00:34,333 --> 00:00:37,302
<i>If you pull it close to you</i>

9
00:00:39,738 --> 00:00:41,831
<i>It will reach you, without a doubt</i>

10
00:00:42,574 --> 00:00:43,871
<i>It will come, closer</i>

11
00:00:44,209 --> 00:00:46,769
<i>Now</i>

12
00:00:54,820 --> 00:01:00,190
<i>We're speeding through life,</i>
<i>squeezing it for all of its worth</i>

13
00:01:00,392 --> 00:01:01,552
<i>Our feet are tied</i>

14
00:01:01,627 --> 00:01:05,427
<i>But we still keep going farther</i>

15
00:01:05,764 --> 00:01:10,963
<i>Even if I take it back, and grasp it</i>

16
00:01:11,236 --> 00:01:12,567
<i>If you're not the one</i>

17
00:01:12,638 --> 00:01:14,037
<i>There will be no meaning</i>

18
00:01:14,106 --> 00:01:20,375
<i>And so we'll go far off into the distance.</i>

19
00:01:30,653 --> 00:01:33,952
Umm, where's the room
that Sasuke's in?

20
00:01:34,123 --> 00:01:36,526
Mr. Sasuke is not allowed
any visitors.

21
00:01:36,526 --> 00:01:39,086
What?! Hey, hey!
What's up with that?!

22
00:01:39,262 --> 00:01:40,695
I'm sorry,
those are the rules.

23
00:01:40,763 --> 00:01:42,025
Why, Sis, tell me why?

24
00:01:42,098 --> 00:01:45,033
Naruto, this is a hospital.
Keep it down.

25
00:01:45,335 --> 00:01:48,498
Say! Say!
I've got a favor to ask!

26
00:01:48,638 --> 00:01:49,900
You don't need to say it all.

27
00:01:50,306 --> 00:01:52,501
Well, I thought it would
come to this so...

28
00:01:52,909 --> 00:01:55,844
I searched for someone
to watch your training.

29
00:01:56,012 --> 00:01:57,343
Why?!

30
00:01:57,413 --> 00:01:59,438
I want you to, Kakashi Sensei!

31
00:01:59,716 --> 00:02:01,684
I have some matters
to take care of.

32
00:02:02,118 --> 00:02:04,313
I don't have time to
trouble myself with you.

33
00:02:06,789 --> 00:02:08,916
Oh! Aha...!

34
00:02:09,626 --> 00:02:12,220
You're going to
train Sasuke, aren't you?!

35
00:02:12,428 --> 00:02:13,952
Well... don't say that.

36
00:02:14,430 --> 00:02:17,593
I found a sensei who's
more reliable than I am!

37
00:02:17,734 --> 00:02:19,599
Well... who is it?

38
00:02:20,470 --> 00:02:21,437
It's me!

39
00:02:21,704 --> 00:02:22,398
Huh?!

40
00:02:23,239 --> 00:02:24,570
Oh!

41
00:02:24,641 --> 00:02:25,471
You!

42
00:02:25,541 --> 00:02:27,304
The Closet Perv!

43
00:02:27,510 --> 00:02:28,534
Such insolence!

44
00:02:29,278 --> 00:02:35,080
Ebisu Returns:
Naruto's Toughest Training Yet!

45
00:02:42,358 --> 00:02:45,020
Ebisu Sensei is
a Closet Perv?

46
00:02:45,561 --> 00:02:49,361
Why's this guy
my training teacher?!

47
00:02:49,666 --> 00:02:52,362
In the first place,
he's weaker than me!

48
00:02:53,269 --> 00:02:54,327
What did you say?

49
00:02:54,404 --> 00:02:56,463
But you see! But you see!

50
00:02:56,539 --> 00:02:59,337
A long time ago,
with my Harem Jutsu, this guy...

51
00:02:59,909 --> 00:03:00,739
<i>Transform!</i>

52
00:03:01,377 --> 00:03:04,904
<i>Master Ebisu! Master Ebisu!</i>

53
00:03:11,754 --> 00:03:12,948
<i>B-By any chance...</i>

54
00:03:16,159 --> 00:03:17,456
Harem Jutsu?

55
00:03:17,527 --> 00:03:20,121
U-Uh... it's nothing!

56
00:03:21,698 --> 00:03:25,498
I'll treat you to and buy you
whatever you want later!

57
00:03:26,035 --> 00:03:28,265
Just be quiet about that!

58
00:03:28,337 --> 00:03:29,531
You better.

59
00:03:30,073 --> 00:03:33,736
Wow, I didn't know you
were acquainted.

60
00:03:35,044 --> 00:03:37,205
Well, they're unsavory ties, but.

61
00:03:38,247 --> 00:03:41,182
<i>How could I ever forget</i>
<i>that humiliation?</i>

62
00:03:42,185 --> 00:03:44,483
But why this guy?

63
00:03:44,954 --> 00:03:46,979
I definitely don't want him to.

64
00:03:47,290 --> 00:03:48,518
Same here.

65
00:03:48,591 --> 00:03:52,228
If it weren't Kakashi's favor,
who'd teach you for the fun of it?

66
00:03:52,228 --> 00:03:53,229
Then don't.

67
00:03:53,229 --> 00:03:54,719
Now now, both of you...

68
00:03:54,797 --> 00:03:56,389
Don't say that.

69
00:03:57,834 --> 00:04:00,428
Naruto, Ebisu Sensei is a private tutor

70
00:04:00,503 --> 00:04:04,269
who teaches the elite,
a special Jonin!

71
00:04:04,407 --> 00:04:07,843
He's truly better
at teaching than I am.

72
00:04:11,681 --> 00:04:15,811
Well, Naruto, of the three kids
in Squad Seven that I taught,

73
00:04:16,018 --> 00:04:18,350
you're the worst at the basic skills.

74
00:04:18,821 --> 00:04:20,846
Get taught with care
this time around.

75
00:04:21,390 --> 00:04:25,952
How the heck am I inferior
compared to Sakura and Sasuke?!

76
00:04:29,565 --> 00:04:33,126
Naruto, it's fact that you
don't have the fundamentals down.

77
00:04:33,603 --> 00:04:36,470
No matter what you do,
the basic skills are important.

78
00:04:37,073 --> 00:04:41,271
If you really want to become strong,
just be quiet and listen to what I say.

79
00:04:45,448 --> 00:04:47,882
Now then, Ebisu Sensei,
I'm leaving him with you.

80
00:04:48,384 --> 00:04:49,408
Yes, yes.

81
00:04:50,219 --> 00:04:50,878
<i>Dang it.</i>

82
00:04:52,955 --> 00:04:54,388
<i>It may appear to be harsh,</i>

83
00:04:54,457 --> 00:04:56,948
<i>but you can become stronger</i>
<i>a lot more.</i>

84
00:04:58,628 --> 00:04:59,754
Do your best.

85
00:05:02,031 --> 00:05:03,999
Okay, then, let's go.

86
00:05:06,969 --> 00:05:08,960
Still, I'm not convinced...

87
00:05:09,272 --> 00:05:09,966
Huh?

88
00:05:10,373 --> 00:05:12,068
You see!

89
00:05:12,141 --> 00:05:14,837
Fundamentals might be important,

90
00:05:14,911 --> 00:05:19,177
but I won't get strong being taught
by someone weaker than me!

91
00:05:19,549 --> 00:05:22,677
So in other words,
you want to say that I'm weak?

92
00:05:22,752 --> 00:05:24,913
Who else is here?!

93
00:05:25,221 --> 00:05:30,318
I was certainly surprised having
that indecent Jutsu used on me that time.

94
00:05:31,027 --> 00:05:35,487
But it's premature for you to
judge my ability on just that.

95
00:05:35,832 --> 00:05:38,494
Even though you were
totally knocked out.

96
00:05:40,870 --> 00:05:41,837
Fine.

97
00:05:42,104 --> 00:05:44,368
Then, why don't we put
it to the test?

98
00:05:44,507 --> 00:05:45,132
Hmm?

99
00:05:45,508 --> 00:05:47,874
Naruto, run.

100
00:05:48,110 --> 00:05:48,735
Huh?

101
00:05:49,312 --> 00:05:55,444
If you can get to outrun me,
I'll back down quietly.

102
00:05:55,952 --> 00:05:57,112
Back down?

103
00:05:57,186 --> 00:05:57,948
Yes.

104
00:05:58,020 --> 00:06:01,581
And of course, I'll speak to
Kakashi Sensei

105
00:06:01,657 --> 00:06:05,184
about you receiving direct training.

106
00:06:05,361 --> 00:06:06,794
What?! Really?!

107
00:06:07,430 --> 00:06:10,763
This elite instructor does not
go back on his word.

108
00:06:11,033 --> 00:06:14,230
However, this is only if
you can outrun me.

109
00:06:14,937 --> 00:06:17,167
Then that makes it easy!

110
00:06:17,807 --> 00:06:18,831
See ya!

111
00:06:29,218 --> 00:06:30,617
This'll be a snap, a snap!

112
00:06:30,953 --> 00:06:35,117
I'll lose that...
Closet Perv in no time!

113
00:06:42,231 --> 00:06:43,721
He already can't catch up!

114
00:06:43,799 --> 00:06:46,859
I knew I was quite
an exceptional Ninja...

115
00:06:46,936 --> 00:06:48,801
Who is exceptional, you say?

116
00:06:53,876 --> 00:06:58,245
Surely you're not thinking you can
outrun me with just that much.

117
00:06:58,881 --> 00:07:00,212
W-What're you saying?!

118
00:07:00,483 --> 00:07:02,280
The chase has still...

119
00:07:04,287 --> 00:07:05,879
only just begun!

120
00:07:23,272 --> 00:07:25,570
Though he's a Closet Perv,

121
00:07:25,641 --> 00:07:28,974
he's the elite tutor after all,
he's good.

122
00:07:32,315 --> 00:07:33,339
Now then.

123
00:08:01,210 --> 00:08:03,337
<i>I knew you were Closet Perv.</i>

124
00:08:07,416 --> 00:08:09,213
What are you doing...?

125
00:08:09,585 --> 00:08:10,711
Naruto?

126
00:08:13,322 --> 00:08:16,382
I see. The idea isn't bad.

127
00:08:17,626 --> 00:08:20,459
Then, how about this?!

128
00:08:20,830 --> 00:08:22,297
Shadow Clone Jutsu!

129
00:08:26,702 --> 00:08:27,600
Heh!

130
00:08:27,737 --> 00:08:31,400
Catch me... if you can!

131
00:08:33,876 --> 00:08:35,776
Not bad...

132
00:08:36,679 --> 00:08:42,447
However, you are not the only one
who uses the Shadow Clone Jutsu.

133
00:08:46,222 --> 00:08:47,587
I won't let you get away!

134
00:08:50,826 --> 00:08:51,884
Dang it!

135
00:08:59,602 --> 00:09:02,070
Son... of... a...!

136
00:09:17,653 --> 00:09:19,416
Now then, next.

137
00:09:22,591 --> 00:09:23,649
Hold it!

138
00:09:32,301 --> 00:09:34,030
I found you!

139
00:09:37,940 --> 00:09:38,964
Wait!

140
00:09:40,042 --> 00:09:41,168
I won't let you
get away!

141
00:09:41,243 --> 00:09:42,073
Get off!

142
00:09:42,411 --> 00:09:44,174
There!
No, actually, here!

143
00:09:44,680 --> 00:09:45,339
Here!

144
00:09:45,981 --> 00:09:46,675
There!

145
00:09:46,949 --> 00:09:47,643
There!

146
00:09:47,917 --> 00:09:49,077
Hold it!

147
00:09:58,060 --> 00:09:59,652
Have you reached your limit?

148
00:10:07,303 --> 00:10:08,702
You're freaking pesky!

149
00:10:08,771 --> 00:10:10,864
Give it up already!

150
00:10:11,006 --> 00:10:13,065
What are you snapping
back at me for?

151
00:10:13,309 --> 00:10:16,335
This is a chase, so chasing
is natural, right?

152
00:10:17,880 --> 00:10:19,711
<i>T-True enough...</i>

153
00:10:20,282 --> 00:10:24,378
Naruto, you have understood
my greatness by now, right?

154
00:10:24,854 --> 00:10:26,754
It's about time you surrendered
and moved on to training

155
00:10:26,822 --> 00:10:28,813
The heck with that!

156
00:10:30,593 --> 00:10:35,792
I'm going to bump you off,
and receive Kakashi Sensei's training!

157
00:10:37,266 --> 00:10:39,291
Even if I have to knock you out!

158
00:10:40,569 --> 00:10:43,367
It appears you still have
some spirit left.

159
00:10:47,943 --> 00:10:50,434
<i>To think he would come at me</i>
<i>head on, even though this is a chase.</i>

160
00:10:50,813 --> 00:10:52,713
<i>Just what I would expect of you, Naruto.</i>

161
00:10:53,282 --> 00:10:57,241
<i>As Kakashi said, he's the</i>
<i>number one unpredictabile Ninja.</i>

162
00:10:57,419 --> 00:10:58,909
Don't take this badly!

163
00:10:58,988 --> 00:10:59,920
Eat this!

164
00:11:03,392 --> 00:11:04,723
<i>Clone Jutsu...?</i>

165
00:11:18,707 --> 00:11:22,666
The game is over, Naruto!

166
00:11:24,513 --> 00:11:25,810
<i>Dang it!</i>

167
00:11:31,419 --> 00:11:34,650
<i>Miso</i> flavor barbecued pork noodles and
salt flavor ramen noodles!

168
00:11:35,690 --> 00:11:36,520
Here you go!

169
00:11:38,393 --> 00:11:41,590
Naruto, having been shown
your movements and

170
00:11:41,696 --> 00:11:45,097
having further analyzed
what Kakashi has told me...

171
00:11:45,467 --> 00:11:49,130
it is clear that you cannot control
Chakra well.

172
00:11:50,672 --> 00:11:51,900
Control...?

173
00:11:52,207 --> 00:11:52,901
That's right.

174
00:11:53,508 --> 00:11:57,069
Now then, comparing you
with Sasuke and Sakura...

175
00:11:57,412 --> 00:12:00,848
I shall explain your
bad points in order.

176
00:12:02,217 --> 00:12:05,618
As you know, in the case of using
Ninjutsu, Genjutsu and the like,

177
00:12:05,687 --> 00:12:08,850
Ninjas build up Chakra and
activate the Jutsu.

178
00:12:08,990 --> 00:12:11,686
I-I know that already!

179
00:12:12,761 --> 00:12:13,591
Is that so?

180
00:12:14,062 --> 00:12:17,327
Then, in the case of comparing
the three of you,

181
00:12:17,399 --> 00:12:21,130
I shall explain specifically
how you are inferior.

182
00:12:21,670 --> 00:12:24,036
That's kind of an irritating
way of saying it.

183
00:12:24,606 --> 00:12:27,074
I'm treating you the ramen
as promised,

184
00:12:27,142 --> 00:12:28,336
so be quiet and listen!

185
00:12:29,711 --> 00:12:33,340
First, let us say that Sakura
uses Clone Jutsu.

186
00:12:33,648 --> 00:12:34,979
Clone Jutsu!

187
00:12:38,787 --> 00:12:43,724
In her case, her build up control as well as
her control of Chakra is perfect,

188
00:12:43,825 --> 00:12:46,658
so she can make clones without
using wasteful energy.

189
00:12:47,529 --> 00:12:48,826
Cha!

190
00:12:49,264 --> 00:12:51,562
Next, in Sasuke's case,

191
00:12:51,800 --> 00:12:54,997
he is somewhat poor at
building up Chakra.

192
00:12:56,604 --> 00:12:57,730
Clone Jutsu.

193
00:13:02,143 --> 00:13:05,374
But, his control of Chakra is perfect,

194
00:13:05,613 --> 00:13:09,743
so both he and Sakura can
make five clones.

195
00:13:10,852 --> 00:13:15,289
But, he uses a bit more wasteful
Chakra than Sakura.

196
00:13:15,623 --> 00:13:16,647
Oh!

197
00:13:16,725 --> 00:13:18,852
So Sasuke's nothing special.

198
00:13:19,127 --> 00:13:23,120
In your case, there's no time
to be laughing at others.

199
00:13:23,365 --> 00:13:24,024
Huh?

200
00:13:26,201 --> 00:13:30,331
You are very poor at building up Chakra
and controlling it,

201
00:13:30,505 --> 00:13:33,269
so you cannot make clones
with the same amount of Chakra.

202
00:13:35,009 --> 00:13:37,443
In the case where you strain to
make clones despite that,

203
00:13:37,512 --> 00:13:42,142
after consuming a much larger amount
of Chakra than Sakura and Sasuke...

204
00:13:42,217 --> 00:13:43,548
Clone Jutsu!

205
00:13:45,854 --> 00:13:49,017
...you can barely make
one clone at best.

206
00:13:50,225 --> 00:13:50,919
By the way,

207
00:13:50,992 --> 00:13:55,053
Sakura and Sasuke can become ten
with the same amount of Chakra.

208
00:14:01,436 --> 00:14:05,930
Like this, the three of you are
this different even using the same Jutsu.

209
00:14:08,143 --> 00:14:12,739
Well, this is a somewhat exaggerated
comparison of you three,

210
00:14:12,814 --> 00:14:16,682
but you build up too much Chakra,
use too much physical strength,

211
00:14:16,751 --> 00:14:19,049
and your Jutsu activation is also unstable.

212
00:14:19,387 --> 00:14:23,323
But, there've been times when
I was greater than Sakura and Sasuke...

213
00:14:23,391 --> 00:14:24,688
That's only because you
happen to have

214
00:14:24,759 --> 00:14:28,593
the most outstanding stamina
of the three!

215
00:14:31,399 --> 00:14:34,095
<i>Well, I am pretty sure that</i>
<i>your Chakra control</i>

216
00:14:34,169 --> 00:14:37,605
<i>is getting difficult due to the influence</i>
<i>of the Nine Tails...</i>

217
00:14:37,672 --> 00:14:40,072
<i>which is the origin of your stamina.</i>

218
00:14:42,410 --> 00:14:45,777
Anyway, there is no mistaking
that you can become strong

219
00:14:45,847 --> 00:14:48,281
if you carry out the training
we will be doing from now.

220
00:14:48,450 --> 00:14:49,883
Huh?! Really?!

221
00:14:50,218 --> 00:14:52,243
I guarantee it.

222
00:14:52,787 --> 00:14:54,345
Now then, let's go!

223
00:14:54,756 --> 00:14:56,383
Sir, your bill.

224
00:14:56,524 --> 00:14:58,219
Oh, that's right.

225
00:14:58,526 --> 00:14:59,458
Wha?!

226
00:15:07,135 --> 00:15:08,625
Thank you very much!

227
00:15:17,812 --> 00:15:19,973
We've come quite a long way...

228
00:15:20,315 --> 00:15:22,408
But, this is a hot spring town, right?

229
00:15:22,984 --> 00:15:26,215
It doesn't look like we've come
here to leisurely soak in a hot spring...

230
00:15:26,488 --> 00:15:29,048
Hey! Naruto!

231
00:15:29,123 --> 00:15:30,522
That's the women's bath!

232
00:15:30,592 --> 00:15:34,028
I simply will not allow
indecent behavior!

233
00:15:35,730 --> 00:15:36,662
<i>Huh?</i>

234
00:15:37,098 --> 00:15:38,531
<i>I'm not you...</i>

235
00:15:38,766 --> 00:15:41,599
<i>It's not that I was trying to peep.</i>
<i>Believe it!</i>

236
00:15:41,803 --> 00:15:45,864
<i>Thinking of something like that</i>
<i>in the first place makes you a Closet Perv!</i>

237
00:15:48,443 --> 00:15:50,206
What's with that look?

238
00:15:50,278 --> 00:15:51,768
N-Nothing.

239
00:15:52,313 --> 00:15:55,043
More importantly, why've we come
to a place like this?!

240
00:15:55,316 --> 00:15:57,716
Will soaking in a hot spring
do anything for training?

241
00:15:58,253 --> 00:15:59,083
No!

242
00:15:59,187 --> 00:16:01,451
The training will be here
in this hot spring area!

243
00:16:06,194 --> 00:16:07,661
Okay, this is the place.

244
00:16:08,263 --> 00:16:10,390
It's a bath, sure enough!

245
00:16:10,765 --> 00:16:12,323
What are you saying?

246
00:16:12,634 --> 00:16:15,125
I said this is training, didn't I?
Training!

247
00:16:15,403 --> 00:16:17,928
We're going to train here?

248
00:16:18,072 --> 00:16:19,664
What the heck are we going to do?

249
00:16:23,077 --> 00:16:26,308
Walk on this hot water!

250
00:16:26,447 --> 00:16:27,471
What?!

251
00:16:29,817 --> 00:16:30,784
What is it?

252
00:16:31,519 --> 00:16:33,680
Walk on hot water?

253
00:16:34,556 --> 00:16:36,888
Can you really do that?

254
00:16:36,958 --> 00:16:38,289
Of course!

255
00:16:39,994 --> 00:16:42,121
I heard from Kakashi Sensei.

256
00:16:42,497 --> 00:16:46,263
You already did tree climbing training
without using your hands, right?

257
00:16:46,501 --> 00:16:47,968
It's an application of that.

258
00:16:48,570 --> 00:16:50,094
Hmm...
What do you mean?

259
00:16:50,305 --> 00:16:53,934
Besides, I don't really remember
stuff from long ago.

260
00:16:54,742 --> 00:16:57,006
In tree climbing, all you do
is accumulate

261
00:16:57,078 --> 00:16:59,512
only the necessary amount of Chakra
in one necessary location

262
00:16:59,581 --> 00:17:02,141
and maintain that amount of
Chakra all the while.

263
00:17:02,216 --> 00:17:05,947
Trees are fixed objects,
so you only need to be attached to it.

264
00:17:07,589 --> 00:17:08,521
In other words,

265
00:17:08,590 --> 00:17:11,855
it's training for building up
a fixed amount of Chakra.

266
00:17:12,794 --> 00:17:14,318
To float on the surface of water,

267
00:17:14,395 --> 00:17:16,522
you have to discharge on
a constant basis

268
00:17:16,598 --> 00:17:18,828
an appropriate amount of Chakra
from your feet to the water

269
00:17:18,900 --> 00:17:22,836
and balance that to the extent that
you can float your own body.

270
00:17:23,538 --> 00:17:24,300
<i>Huh?</i>

271
00:17:24,372 --> 00:17:28,706
This Chakra control is
more difficult than maintaining...

272
00:17:28,876 --> 00:17:33,176
and is a control training for
discharge and usage of fixed amount

273
00:17:33,247 --> 00:17:35,272
of Chakra for Jutsu and alike.

274
00:17:35,583 --> 00:17:38,279
Hmm, I really don't get it!

275
00:17:38,653 --> 00:17:41,781
Well, it would be better to
show you in your case.

276
00:17:42,523 --> 00:17:44,821
First, you build up Chakra
in your feet.

277
00:17:46,928 --> 00:17:50,295
Then, while constantly discharging
a fixed amount...

278
00:17:50,365 --> 00:17:52,697
you balance it with your body weight.

279
00:17:56,337 --> 00:17:57,634
And...

280
00:17:57,705 --> 00:17:59,502
well, this is how it goes.

281
00:17:59,574 --> 00:18:03,908
Oh! Okay!
I'm going to try!

282
00:18:04,379 --> 00:18:06,244
First, you build up Chakra
in your feet.

283
00:18:08,549 --> 00:18:09,516
Then!

284
00:18:09,617 --> 00:18:11,551
Discharge a fixed amount. Right?

285
00:18:11,653 --> 00:18:12,677
Oh!

286
00:18:13,154 --> 00:18:14,143
I knew it.

287
00:18:14,322 --> 00:18:16,085
Hot-hot-hot-hot!

288
00:18:17,091 --> 00:18:19,719
I forgot to mention it,
but this hot water is 60° C (140° F).

289
00:18:20,061 --> 00:18:21,961
If you do nothing but fail...

290
00:18:22,030 --> 00:18:24,157
you will become a boiled octopus!

291
00:18:24,432 --> 00:18:25,626
Dang it!

292
00:18:27,201 --> 00:18:28,930
<i>I'll do it no matter what!</i>

293
00:18:45,219 --> 00:18:49,053
You're unusually spirited today,
honored grandson!

294
00:18:51,025 --> 00:18:54,552
<i>My principle of guidance</i>
<i>has finally gotten through!</i>

295
00:18:55,396 --> 00:18:57,387
This would ordinarily be the
time to go carry out

296
00:18:57,465 --> 00:18:59,399
a surprise attack on Lord Hokage.

297
00:19:00,234 --> 00:19:02,202
I've stopped doing that now!

298
00:19:02,670 --> 00:19:03,871
That's right!

299
00:19:03,871 --> 00:19:05,862
So you have finally understood.

300
00:19:06,107 --> 00:19:10,441
That the shortcut to becoming
the Hokage is to do as I say...

301
00:19:11,112 --> 00:19:13,012
There are no shortcuts!

302
00:19:13,748 --> 00:19:14,339
Huh?

303
00:19:15,783 --> 00:19:17,375
Brother Naruto said it...

304
00:19:19,120 --> 00:19:23,147
If you're to become Hokage,
be prepared for that!

305
00:19:27,795 --> 00:19:28,693
Oh!

306
00:19:31,065 --> 00:19:32,760
I'm starting to get it!

307
00:19:34,102 --> 00:19:38,869
<i>To think he would get the</i>
<i>hang of the Chakra control this quickly...</i>

308
00:19:39,474 --> 00:19:42,341
<i>I never thought,</i>
<i>you would grow this much.</i>

309
00:19:43,311 --> 00:19:46,712
<i>Indeed, there are no shortcuts,</i>
<i>in anything...</i>

310
00:19:47,749 --> 00:19:50,377
<i>It appears I had the</i>
<i>wrong idea about you...</i>

311
00:19:50,651 --> 00:19:53,882
<i>You are a much smarter teacher</i>
<i>than I am.</i>

312
00:19:55,056 --> 00:19:58,321
<i>And, you were not just a Demon Fox...</i>

313
00:19:59,260 --> 00:20:02,457
<i>You were a splendid</i>
<i>Hidden Leaf Village Ninja!</i>

314
00:20:02,530 --> 00:20:05,658
Oh! Hot!

315
00:20:05,733 --> 00:20:07,223
Hm?! That is!

316
00:20:12,807 --> 00:20:16,971
Humph! I don't know who you are
or where you're from, but...

317
00:20:17,845 --> 00:20:21,042
I will not allow indecency!

318
00:20:22,416 --> 00:20:23,314
Man...

319
00:20:25,419 --> 00:20:26,852
T-That is!

320
00:20:28,823 --> 00:20:29,721
What?!

321
00:20:41,068 --> 00:20:42,695
Don't make a ruckus.

322
00:20:43,070 --> 00:20:46,369
Jeez, it won't do to be found out!

323
00:20:50,545 --> 00:20:53,036
<i>The Closet Perv lost?</i>

324
00:20:54,849 --> 00:20:58,785
