335
00:22:03,690 --> 00:22:09,720
<i>All over the world, the sky's smiling,</i>
<i>so look up and smile too</i>

336
00:22:09,796 --> 00:22:17,134
<i>Oh yeah! Oh yeah! Oh yeah!</i>
<i>Fight! Fight! Fight!</i>

337
00:22:17,237 --> 00:22:23,665
<i>All over the world, the sky's smiling,</i>
<i>so look up and smile too</i>

338
00:22:23,743 --> 00:22:30,911
<i>Oh yeah! Oh yeah! Oh yeah!</i>
<i>Fight! Fight! Fight!</i>

339
00:22:37,690 --> 00:22:39,851
Hey, hey, hey, hey, you!

340
00:22:39,959 --> 00:22:42,553
